And this [link](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/28877857/transactional-spring-mybatis-not-working)&lt;br/&gt;

***read-only*** used for optimizing of our application.&lt;br&gt;
Your connection pool decides which connections to use in order to execute your queries.&lt;br&gt;
Also you can try something like the below code &amp;ndash; maybe it will work for you if you apply it to your method.

```
@Transactional
public class MyClass {
    ...
